data.description: Now Selling - Acacia by Woodside Homes is one of the newest neighborhoods to come to Sommers Bend, the new master-planned community in Temecula everyone is talking about! The single-family detached homes are artfully set in this ideal place that has it all, from a state-of-the-art community hub and miles of open space for exploring the great outdoors, to all the nearby schools, shopping, dining and entertainment you could dream of. Woodside Homes has incorporated Lifestyle Solutions into these homes based on full collaboration with insight groups for healthy living and today's latest technologies. Included are "drop zones" with USB charging stations, low maintenance features, and functional flex space for dedicated office and exercise rooms, lofts, spa-inspired Primary baths, and extra storage space throughout the home. Single level living offers simplistic elegance in three to four bedrooms and three to three-and-a-half bath floor plans, and two-story homes present four to five bedrooms and three-and-a-half to four-and-half baths, ranging in size from 3,058 to 4,524 interior square feet. This new neighborhood will connect you to everything you love. Sign up on the interest list for Acacia today to receive the latest updates and priority announcements!
